data.name: TextBox1.Text
data.value:
This tool identifies perfect-match bits (bits that are always on in vehicles with the selected feature, and off in vehicles without the selected feature).
To identify the bits for Engine Hours, I searched 2013 Taurus and Interceptor for the feature "Hourmeter". The program identified two "Perfect Bits" in the IPC module. Enabling those bits enabled the Engine Hours counters in my car.
This is a statistical analysis and only identifies consistencies -- not guarantees.
